to make their own personal

00:00:07.480 --> 00:00:08.280 align:middle line:90%
contact.

00:00:08.280 --> 00:00:09.720 align:middle line:84%
Do you think this
is a good idea?

00:00:09.720 --> 00:00:11.820 align:middle line:90%
