but also spiritually.

00:00:44.520 --> 00:00:46.620 align:middle line:10%
>> On the "Arc of Time."

00:00:46.620 --> 00:00:50.880 align:middle line:84%
>> Human beings, are we just
machine of flesh and blood,

00:00:50.880 --> 00:00:52.710 align:middle line:90%
